o me :). \n\nI am attaching the patch anyway if you folks think it is a nice optimization - this way the node can join right away instead of having to wait for the timeout and start a new election.\n\nI'll close the Jira.\n\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=vishal.k","name":"vishal.k","key":"vishal.k","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Vishal Kathuria","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2011-05-26T18:09:31.479+0000","updated":"2011-05-26T18:09:31.479+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12508358/comment/13039849","id":"13039849","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=vishal.k","name":"vishal.k","key":"vishal.k","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Vishal Kathuria","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"This is a simple patch to optimize the case when a server that would restore the quorum is coming up.\n\nInstead of leader giving up and leader election happening, this change will make the new server join the existing ensemble.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=vishal.k","name":"vishal.k","key":"vishal.k","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=smal